within the Ancestral Hall.

59
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:23,110
You'll be the first woman

60
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,830
the Ning Family's ancestral hall.

61
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,830
The Nings will honor you always.

62
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,480
Father.

63
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,040
Father.

64
