Father.

65
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,760
Father!

66
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:42,900
Father...

67
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:48,830
Bingqing, don't let me down.

68
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,800
Father.

69
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,320
