77
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,270
you are daughter to me, the Duke Ning.

78
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,550
You carry the honor of the Ning Family.

79
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:41,070
Nothing matters more than this.

80
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,280
