118
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:14,720
I...

119
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:17,510
I only sought justice for myself.

120
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,190
One day, revenge comes to an end.

121
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:25,630
When that day comes, what will you do?

122
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,320
I...

123
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,030
(My parents are gone.)

124
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,550
(Jiang Village is no more.)

125
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,310
(I have nowhere to turn.)

126
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,790
