127
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,470
(What could I possibly do?)

128
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:43,510
Perhaps marry, tend to a home,
raise children.

129
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,590
My grandson

130
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,830
is truly devoted to you.

131
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:53,270
Jingchu treats me with utmost kindness.

132
00:09:53,570 --> 00:09:54,410
He does.

133
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,790
Jingchu is indeed a good child.

134
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,110
But sadly,

135
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:02,590
his birth mother was a palace maid.

136
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:05,630
Back then, the Emperor was drunk,

137
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,710
and showed her favor.

138
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,830
When he sobered up,
he was furious,

139
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,710
so he kept his distance
from Jingchu as well.

140
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,950
Even the eunuchs dared to mistreat him.

141
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,710
Thankfully, he stands strong.

142
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,310
Why did you kill the Chief Eunuch?

143
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:24,070
You must already know

144
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:27,190
why the Emperor
doesn't accept you as his son.

145
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,870
Yet he holds great power.

146
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,400
Aren't you afraid?

147
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,830
But I wish to live.

148
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:35,950
Power is no reason to bully the weak.

149
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,390
No matter who he is, I'll resist.

150
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:41,310
(His gaze is steadfast.)

151
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,090
(He stands firm before power.)

152
00:10:43,680 --> 00:10:44,830
(I can tell that in time,)

153
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,630
