183
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:56,630
Your Majesty,

184
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,190
Jingchu has shown me true devotion.

185
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:01,870
Yet why must a woman's fate

186
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,790
always be to live in someone's shadow?

187
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:06,870
Given this chance to start again,

188
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,910
I no longer accept such fate,

189
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:09,830
nor will I bow to it.

190
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:12,150
So, Your Majesty,

191
