195
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:31,150
I wish to make my mark in court,

196
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,030
to speak

197
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:35,830
for those like me,

198
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:38,670
the women who suffer in silence.

199
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:42,510
Well said.

200
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:45,520
Stand up.

201
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:50,190
Good child, I knew you wouldn't fail me.

202
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:54,790
Thank you, Your Majesty.

203
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:03,070
By the Mandate of Heaven,
an edict from the Emperor.

204
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:07,470
Jiang Leyao of the Ning Family
is kind-hearted,

205
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:08,950
and outstanding in talent.

206
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:12,870
