207
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:15,350
as Lady Inspector of the Dali Court,

208
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:17,870
in charge of all matters
concerning women.

209
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:20,830
She must investigate
every case with care,

210
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,630
and discern the finest details.

211
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:25,390
Let no injustice hide in the shadows.

212
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:28,430
Let the truth shine
before all under heaven.

213
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:30,230
So decreed.

214
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:33,190
I thank His Majesty for this grace.

215
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,360
Everyone,

216
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,670
from today, I, Jiang Leyao,

217
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:57,870
will not bow to the powerful,

218
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,230
nor fear the influential.

219
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:01,910
I will speak for
women wronged and unheard,

220
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:04,990
and uphold justice in this vast world.

221
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:06,870
Thank you, Madam.

